    "name": "Bouncy Escape",
    "steam_appid": 3256880,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>准备好跳跃吧！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256880/extras/b27a61a46f457a3bab70fdfee98885d4.avif?t=1743991824\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256880/extras_big/b27a61a46f457a3bab70fdfee98885d4.avif?t=1743991824 width=800 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跳入<strong>BOUNCY ESCAPE！</strong>的多彩世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跑、跳并在多个游戏模式中超越其他玩家——你会选择什么？跑酷比赛？相扑对决？足球？还是在无尽的街道上混乱奔跑，躲避汽车？与最多四名玩家[ b]本地或在线[/b]游玩。准备好！倒计时开始，<strong>3...2...1...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级并在其他玩家中脱颖而出</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赢得一轮？赚取<strong>金币</strong>! 在商店中使用它们购买双跳，使自己比对手更强...或者你宁愿使用表情符号来表达你对其他玩家的感受？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与朋友和家人一起玩</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由你决定如何玩——<strong>本地</strong>分屏，还是<strong>在线</strong>与朋友或其他玩家？你可以创建一个仅限受邀玩家的私人房间，或者加入一个公共房间，与来自世界各地的玩家竞争！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无尽的冒险</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们为你准备了很多游戏模式和地图，让乐趣永不无聊……你会在哪张地图上表现得最好？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256880/extras/f4c85e2ebfb263373b20ef7fe2401eb0.avif?t=1743991824\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256880/extras_big/f4c85e2ebfb263373b20ef7fe2401eb0.avif?t=1743991824 width=800 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BOUNCY RACE <i>(本地和在线)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3...2...1... 谁会第一个到达终点？在这张漂浮的地图上，任何人都有可能掉入深渊……你能克服所有障碍，越过<strong>终点线</strong>吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256880/extras/7a71251f549877d5b296494ba84d4272.avif?t=1743991824\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256880/extras_big/7a71251f549877d5b296494ba84d4272.avif?t=1743991824 width=800 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CROSS THE ROAD <i>(本地和在线)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >交通混乱等着你！<strong>冲刺</strong>穿越无尽的道路，躲避快速行驶的汽车，千万不要被压扁！你走得越远，难度就越大。你能超过你的朋友，成为终极过街者吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256880/extras/899ccd18ea6d3bd3badda7a6ab190410.avif?t=1743991824\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256880/extras_big/899ccd18ea6d3bd3badda7a6ab190410.avif?t=1743991824 width=800 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FLOOR FALL <i>(本地和在线)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地面在你脚下崩溃！<strong>跑、跳和躲避</strong>，避免掉入深渊，随着地板一块一块地消失。你能比其他玩家活得更久，成为最后一个站着的人吗？你生存得越久，体验就越强烈！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256880/extras/0adb9bb300aef1058f46988e0dfe3623.avif?t=1743991824\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256880/extras_big/0adb9bb300aef1058f46988e0dfe3623.avif?t=1743991824 width=800 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GOAL RUSH <i>(本地和在线)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个人都喜欢运动……两个球门、两个队伍和一个球！哪个队伍能进更多球，赢得<strong>足球</strong>对决？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256880/extras/9c38f8c77d06d60b38c384986f92bc9a.avif?t=1743991824\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256880/extras_big/9c38f8c77d06d60b38c384986f92bc9a.avif?t=1743991824 width=800 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SUMO <i>(本地)</i><br>时间紧迫……平台正在缩小！你能将所有玩家推下去，成为<strong>相扑王</strong>吗？只有一个胜者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256880/extras/61f3cbff7d306648882459d5161ac734.avif?t=1743991824\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256880/extras_big/61f3cbff7d306648882459d5161ac734.avif?t=1743991824 width=800 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ENDLESS RUN <i>(本地)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能跳过多少个平台？这个无尽的随机生成世界将考验你！选择最适合你的游戏类型……提升你角色的神秘助推器？还是你想在计时模式下<strong>挑战</strong>自己，看看你能在规定时间内跳过多少个平台？是时候做决定了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
